{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-05129/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-05129"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:51:29"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Duration"]},"value":{"none":["long take"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman stares up at a man altering the dress she wears."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-05129","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-05129"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1/6de15259-4002-4ac8-81c9-0fe6aaa7b11c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:55:08.534Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Barbara tries to connect with Reynolds by matching his eyeline. He rebuffs these attempts, signaling his refusal of emotional engagement and insistence on confining his involvement with her to the work.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:197.40952732644004,306.1429098966026,1232.6165528064996,438.1704671344166"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1/425ae2ff-6d60-4742-a98e-3f46d877d06f","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:55:29.918Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds shares this reticence to be in the spotlight with Cristóbal Balenciaga, who served as one source of inspiration for PTA when crafting his character: “[Balenciaga] didn’t follow the scene because he <em>was</em> the scene. He demanded that his designs, not himself, get the attention, which led to misunderstandings and a good deal of myth making from fashion editors in need of copy and from clients he refused to meet” (Blume, <em>The Master of Us All</em>, 5).</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05129/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:27.861903423303715,28.52468336344618,308.77954209748896,225.75470827178725"}}}]}]}]}